| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5029 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9db8e392-ce4e-5138-9cfc-679bd7c5b874"
